T1  - Hysterosalpingographic Findings Among Ghanaian Women with Infertility: A Five-year Trend Analysis
A1  - Edzie E.K.M.
A1  - Dzefi-Tettey K.
A1  - Gorleku P.N.
A1  - Brakohiapa E.K.K.
